{
  "stem": "21308.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just got here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, oh, fair enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we were young, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bright, and we-- we had-- we were elan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what I mean, elan?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he turned to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, well, my parting advice to you is if you can sort out this bleeding mess, you deserve a bloody knighthood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what he said to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you can sort out this bleeding mess, you deserve a bloody knighthood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now you don't get that said to you every day of the week, so you remember that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And anyway, I drove around, and it was clear to me that it was a Kriegsmarine [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was Kriegsmarine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because when I looked in buildings, I saw sectionized pieces of submarine control chambers and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It'd obviously been very well maintained, but of course all the public utilities had been destroyed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Water, gas, all that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I did a bit of hard thinking, and I was a professional soldier.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I got on the blower to my people, and I got my whole group forward, which included my sergeant major.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By this time, I had picked up a little Dutch Jew whose name was Hubert Steinberg, and I spoke to you about him yesterday.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Hubert came out of the clink, the German civvie clink.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he'd been in Stutthof concentration camp, and he'd been a prisoner along with his brother and his mom and dad on the [INAUDIBLE], which was one of the burning ships.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I learned afterwards that he actually saw the SS murder his parents by clubbing them with the butt of the rifle.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
